Nothing.

376
00:21:06,320 --> 00:21:09,520
Dad, mom!

377
00:21:09,520 --> 00:21:13,520
Quick, tell me what you were talking about?

378
00:21:13,520 --> 00:21:16,820
I was just telling her that for a first rate lawyer,

379
00:21:16,820 --> 00:21:18,620
