00:21:47,320 --> 00:21:49,120
Well, I'll be seeing you.

391
00:21:49,120 --> 00:21:51,520
Mom!

392
00:21:51,520 --> 00:21:53,520
Don't you ever show your face again!

393
00:21:53,520 --> 00:21:56,420
For goodness sakes, dad, you're a fool, a fool!

